    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process of gilding the edges of a book with a piece of paper laid over the gold and the burnisher rubbed over the paper, resulting in a dull finish.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
